Enum GameFunctions.Action

    public static enum GameFunctions.Action
extends java.lang.Enum<GameFunctions.Action>
    Enumeration of all possible actions the GameFunctions-class offers to external users.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      GAME_EXIT
      Exits the game.
